</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-79_ pf-text-1">Provide ongoing training and support for employees involved in accident recording and first aid provision.








</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-81_ pf-text-1">Encourage reporting and investigation of near misses to identify potential hazards before they escalate into accidents.









